    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Sorry for the short response before. \n\nI'm completly +1on having possibility to add that, but I think it shoudl be a list. \nAlso I think the all [Loaders](http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/api/#loaders) should be configurable, and I'm in particular wondering if we shoudln't use [PackageLoader](http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/api/#jinja2.PackageLoader) instead of [FileSystemLoader](http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/api/#jinja2.FileSystemLoader).\n\nMy take on that would be to use a [ChoiceLoader](http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/api/#jinja2.ChoiceLoader) which as by default our current FileSystemLoader as last search place and allow user to pass custom other loader that have higher priorities.\n\nThought ?\n"
  },
