    "body": "Like @minrk mentioned, this conflicts with #3546 (now merged).  Also, it would probably be a better idea to use a ChoiceLoader like @Carreau mentioned.  \n\nOne thing to keep in mind is that different exporters may have different default paths.  For example, none of the latex templates would be affected by this change (see exporters/latex.py).\n"
